snippet.title: [URDU] 2025 PMGC League | Last Chance | Day 1 | PUBG MOBILE Global Championship
snippet.description:
Khush aam deed 2025 k PUBG MOBILE GLOBAL CHAMPIONSHIP k Last Chance main! Ajj last chance ka pehla din hai.
Han Yahi hai wo Last Chance , jahan na koi ghalti ki gunjaish hai or na koi hifaazti bandh.
Sirf do teamain apna raasta Grand Finals tak bana payengi, or baaqi sab ghar wapis jayengi.

Grand Finals tak ka safar har match ke saath aur mushkil hota jae ga, to apni kursi ki peti baandh lijiye, snacks haath mein lijiye, aur tayyar ho jao haqeeqi junoon aur adrenaline ke liye. 🏆🔥

Is saal ka format dobara badla gaya hai taa k shaiqeen aur waqar k peche bhagny wali teamain dono ko zyada lutf haasil ho.
Pehla bara twist "The Gauntlet Stage" hai, 
Duniya ki 16 behtareen teamain yahan bary dao laga kr muqabla karen gi.
Dao Pech? Har mumkin lagaye jayen gy.

Rank 1 ta 7: Seedha Grand Finals mein pohanch jayen gi.
Rank 8 ta 16: Group Stage se ek aur mauqa hasil ho ga.

Group Stage mai har group se upper ki 3 teamain seedha Grand Finals ke liye qualify kr jayen gi.
Jo teamain 4th–11th par thin unko Last Chance khelny ka akhri mauqa mile ga.
Lekin jo 12th–16th par aayegi, unka 2025 PMGC ka safar yahin khatam ho jayega.
Aakhir mein, Last Chance (Dec 6 ta 7) teamon k liye aakhri parao hoga.

Yahan do din, or do mawaqy hongy.
Top 2 spots hasil karen, ya shaiqeen k sath beth kr Grand Finals ka nazara dekhen.

Khush aamdeed, 2025 PUBG MOBILE GLOBAL CHAMPIONSHIP Mai — Jahan sarbulandi hasil krny k liye ek Faisla Kun Jung Hogi!

Abhi PUBG MOBILE khelen:  https://pubgmobile.go.link/25pmgc
💰Kul Inaami Raqam : Eight hundred forty seven million PKR - 3,000,000$

🗓️ The Gauntlet : 24 Nov  - 26 Nov

Group Green🟢 : 28 - 30 Nov

🗓️ Grand Finals : 12 - 14 Dec

localized.title: [URDU] 2025 PMGC League | Last Chance | Day 1 | PUBG MOBILE Global Championship
localized.description:
Khush aam deed 2025 k PUBG MOBILE GLOBAL CHAMPIONSHIP k Last Chance main! Ajj last chance ka pehla din hai.
Han Yahi hai wo Last Chance , jahan na koi ghalti ki gunjaish hai or na koi hifaazti bandh.
Sirf do teamain apna raasta Grand Finals tak bana payengi, or baaqi sab ghar wapis jayengi.

Grand Finals tak ka safar har match ke saath aur mushkil hota jae ga, to apni kursi ki peti baandh lijiye, snacks haath mein lijiye, aur tayyar ho jao haqeeqi junoon aur adrenaline ke liye. 🏆🔥

Is saal ka format dobara badla gaya hai taa k shaiqeen aur waqar k peche bhagny wali teamain dono ko zyada lutf haasil ho.
Pehla bara twist "The Gauntlet Stage" hai, 
Duniya ki 16 behtareen teamain yahan bary dao laga kr muqabla karen gi.
Dao Pech? Har mumkin lagaye jayen gy.

Rank 1 ta 7: Seedha Grand Finals mein pohanch jayen gi.
Rank 8 ta 16: Group Stage se ek aur mauqa hasil ho ga.

Group Stage mai har group se upper ki 3 teamain seedha Grand Finals ke liye qualify kr jayen gi.
Jo teamain 4th–11th par thin unko Last Chance khelny ka akhri mauqa mile ga.
Lekin jo 12th–16th par aayegi, unka 2025 PMGC ka safar yahin khatam ho jayega.
Aakhir mein, Last Chance (Dec 6 ta 7) teamon k liye aakhri parao hoga.

Yahan do din, or do mawaqy hongy.
Top 2 spots hasil karen, ya shaiqeen k sath beth kr Grand Finals ka nazara dekhen.

Khush aamdeed, 2025 PUBG MOBILE GLOBAL CHAMPIONSHIP Mai — Jahan sarbulandi hasil krny k liye ek Faisla Kun Jung Hogi!

snippet.title: The Boys - Final Season Teaser Trailer | Prime Video
snippet.description:
This is the teaser trailer for The Boys Season 5. It’s Homelander’s world, completely subject to his erratic, egomaniacal whims. Hughie, Mother’s Milk, and Frenchie are imprisoned in a “Freedom Camp.” Annie struggles to mount a resistance against the overwhelming Supe force. Kimiko is nowhere to be found. But when Butcher reappears, ready and willing to use a virus that will wipe all Supes off the map, he sets in motion a chain of events that will forever change the world and everyone in it. It’s the climax, people. Big stuff’s gonna happen April 8 on Prime.

» Watch The Boys on Prime Video: https://amzn.to/2SQdfsv

It's the powerless against the super powerful as The Boys embark on a heroic quest to expose the truth about “The Seven,” and their formidable Vought backing.

snippet.title: India’s Biggest Blockbuster Is Back in cinemas — ‘Sholay - The Final Cut’ 12th Dec release worldwide
snippet.description:
India’s Biggest Blockbuster Is Back in cinemas — ‘Sholay - The Final Cut’ 12th Dec release worldwide

Presenting the trailer of Sholay: The Final Cut.
Restored in 4K & Dolby 5.1, and releasing on 12th December 2025, this is the first-ever theatrical presentation of the original uncut version. As we celebrate 50 years of Sholay, we are honoured to bring this timeless classic back to cinemas for audiences old and new.

Produced by Sippy Films · Directed by Ramesh Sippy · Restored by Film Heritage Foundation
Releasing theatrically via PEN Marudhar.

#SholayTheFinalCut #SholayOn12Dec #SholayTrailer

Film cast : Amitabh Bachchan, Dharmendra, Hema Malini, Sanjeev Kumar, Amjad Khan, Jaya Bachchan, A K Hangal, Satyen Kappu, Mac Mohan, Sachin Pilgaonkar, Jagdeep, Asrani, Leela Mishra, Iftekhar, Om Shiv Puri, Viju Khote, Vikas Anand, Keshto Mukherjee, Mushtaq Merchant, Gita Siddharth, Helen, Jalal Aga, Birbal, Jairaj, Master Alankar, Raj Kishore, Sharad Kumar, Bhanumati, Rajesh, Darshan, Rajan Kapoor, Habib, Surender, Bhagwan Sinha, Jerry Dsouza, Kedar, Saigal, Rajeshwari, Krishna, Girija

 In the village of Ramgarh, retired police chief Thakur Baldev Singh (Sanjeev Kumar) plots to bring down the notorious bandit Gabbar Singh (Amjad Khan) and enlists the help of two lesser criminals, Jai (Amitabh Bachchan) and Veeru (Dharmendra). When Gabbar attacks the village, however, Jai and Veeru wonder why Thakur does nothing to help them. They soon learn that he has no arms, and that Gabbar was the one who cut them off. Enraged by this, they redouble their efforts to help.
